OL,6,FA romance scammer conned an elderly
OL,7,Fpensioner out of more than #20,000
OL,8,Fafter contacting her while playing the
OL,9,Fword game Scrabble online.
OL,11,FThe 83-year-old widow, from Oldham,
OL,12,Ffell for the fraudster after he posed
OL,13,Fas an American millionaire who offered
OL,14,Fher another chance at love later in
OL,15,Flife.
OL,17,FPolice say the conman claimed to be
OL,18,Faged 60 and said he would come to the
OL,19,FUK to be with the woman, who isn't
OL,20,Fbeing identified.
