OL,3,C'Scrabble' romance scammer conned
OL,4,Celderly pensioner out of #20,000
OL,6,FHe persuaded the victim to chat with
OL,7,Fhim on a messaging platform, separate
OL,8,Fto the game, before intensifying the
OL,9,Frelationship and asking for money.
OL,11,FOne request for funds stated that his
OL,12,Fdaughter urgently needed an operation
OL,13,Fon her leg and that he could not pay
OL,14,Fthe surgeon as he did not have access
OL,15,Fto his bank card.
