OL,3,C'Scrabble' romance scammer conned
OL,4,Celderly pensioner out of #20,000
OL,6,F"The photos and videos that she
OL,7,Freceived seemed genuine but I found
OL,8,Fout how to do a reverse image search
OL,9,Fand was able to show her they were all
OL,10,Ffake."
OL,12,FPolice said the woman's brother now
OL,13,Fhas power of attorney and supports her
OL,14,Fbank in investigating suspicious
OL,15,Ftransactions.
OL,17,FThe scammer, or scammers, have not yet
OL,18,Fbeen caught.
