OL,3,C'Scrabble' romance scammer conned
OL,4,Celderly pensioner out of #20,000
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Stacey Shannon, of
OL,7,FGreater Manchester Police said:
OL,8,F"Unfortunately, his story is far from
OL,9,Funique and there are many people who
OL,10,Ffall victim to such scams.
OL,12,F"I hope his experience will help other
OL,13,Fvictims realise what is happening to
OL,14,Fthem and encourage them to make a
OL,15,Freport.
OL,17,F"Everyone should be vigilant online,
OL,18,Fand I want to emphasise that if it
OL,19,Fsounds too good to be true, it
OL,20,Fprobably is."
